  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this lady member of parliament wanted to introduce a new method of killing animals by such a-- it's not a bullet, but something which was on a spring and was hitting the head of the-- specific place on the head-- of the animal, and the animal would immediately die.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then the throat would be cut, and so on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the-- but the Jewish people who were-- well, even the-- even the whole population, the Jewish population, didn't want to agree to it because they want to stick to their-- to their ritual slaughtering of animals.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was a lot of screaming and so on in-- in parliament, and even the whole Polish population was participating in this controversy.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Beg your pardon?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was in 19-- 1938. 1938.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Just before the war.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of course, in Poland, there was some kind-- some groups or-- or-- groups or parties, far right parties, which were copying methods of-- of Nazis.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were not powerful, and they were not dominating, of course.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I would say that the majority of the Pole-- people-- Polish population was not willing to-- to accept those things, but as in all-- in every nation, there are some people, groups, which are-- which are who are accepting such methods.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I remember some accident-- not accident, some, you know-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] At that time we were living in city Ostrow Mazowiecka, where I was attending gymnasium, the high school.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And as usual, at the high school we had some after classes activities.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And in my age, in my grade at that time, we had also the military, paramilitary, training.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Some activities.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
